"Heads start" should also work for "girls start".

sdr> /program=Program.A2;
A2
sdr> heads half sashay
| 4B>  3Bv  3Gv  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1G^  1B^  2B<
sdr> circle left 3/8
|      1Gv  4Gv
| 
| 1B>            4B<
| 
| 2B>            3B<
| 
|      2G^  3G^
sdr> as couples ladies in men sashay
|      1Gv  4Gv
| 
| 3B>            2B<
| 
| 4B>            1B<
| 
|      2G^  3G^
sdr> girls lead right
| 3B>  1G<  2G>  2B<
| 
| 4B>  4G<  3G>  1B<
sdr> /exit
